---
title: Buffalo Chicken Ranch Wraps with Mixed Greens & Cheddar Cheese
description: Spicy buffalo sauce and cooling ranch dressing are a match made in heaven! For this speedy wrap, chicken is tossed in buttery Frank’s hot sauce, then rolled up in tortillas with mixed greens, cheddar cheese, and buttermilk ranch. Spicy, tangy, creamy, and quick—it’s all your wildest lunch dreams come true.
